page_0:
"ATTENTION!

Due to recent cave-ins in the ancient sections of the crypt, the entrance is to remain closed and locked until further notice. The key is currently in possession of High Priest Rieleg. In case of urgency, thou canst ask him to open the entrance for thee, but keep in mind what hath occurred to Brother Sorven. An additional key was given to the late Lord Farrington's death watch.


P.S.: Brother Sorven's body will be retrieved as soon as there is no more imminent danger of another collapse."